Titolo: Konami's Ping Pong

Anno: 1985

Descrizione: Konami's Ping Pong is a sports arcade game created in 1985 by Konami. It is the first video game to accurately reflect the gameplay of table tennis, as opposed to earlier simplifications like Pong. It was ported to the Amstrad CPC, Commodore 64, Famicom Disk System, MSX, and ZX Spectrum.

Genere: Sports 

Valutazione: N/A
